[0.006, "o", "      * Website: \u001b[0;37mhttps://cisofy.com/lynis/controls/FILE-7524/\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[0.080, "o", "  \u001b[1;33m*\u001b[0m One or more sysctl values differ from the scan profile and could be tweaked [KRNL-6000] \r\n"]
[0.002, "o", "    - Solution : Change sysctl value or disable test (skip-test=KRNL-6000:<sysctl-key>)\r\n    - Related resources\r\n"]
[0.025, "o", "      * Article: \u001b[0;36mLinux hardening with sysctl settings\u001b[0m: https://linux-audit.com/linux-hardening-with-sysctl/\r\n"]
